::Primal Prime::

    He was walking around the new base to get his bearings. He knew the Ark 
had to be protected at all costs. At one time in his walking around he got a 
sence that something urgent was happening, but he didn't know what. He went 
to talk with Ramulus.
    Once he found him he tried to describe the feeling he was having. "It 
feels like, well I can't really describe it, all I know is that something is 
very wrong."
